List a user's github repository

Source: R/gh_repos.R
gh_repos_list.Rd

List a user's github repository

gh_repos_list(user, ...)

Arguments

user

The GitHub user
...

Additional parameters, see https://docs.github.com/en/rest

Value

Repositories for the specified user.

See also

Other Repositories: gh_repos_create(), gh_repos_delete_internal(), gh_repos_delete(), gh_repos_mutate()

Examples

gh_repos_list("jdtrat")
